# {{context|uncountable|British|NZ|accounting|lang=en}} The function of compiling and providing financial information primarily by reports referred to as financial statements. Accounting includes bookkeeping, systems design, analysis and interpretation of accounting information.
# {{context|countable|accounting|lang=en}} A company or organisation that performs such a function.

